          "id": "medmcqa-9d193952-cd22-4aab-a77e-c28dbfa697ea",
          "text": "A patient present with lower gastrointestinal bleed. Sigmoidoscopy shows ulcers inthe sigmoid. Biopsy from this area shows flask-shaped ulcers. Which of the following is the most appropriate treatment -",
