          "id": "medmcqa-ff38bdb0-fdf4-41cd-838b-fb9bc8261d2f",
          "text": "When evaluating an ABG from a client with a subdural hematoma, the nurse notes the PaCO2 is 30 mm Hg. Which of the following responses best describes this result?",
