          "correctOptionId": "opt-3",
          "explanation": "Deficiency in CAH Glucocoicoid Mineralocoicoid Androgens 21 hydroxylase Reduced Reduced Increased 3 b hydroxyl-steroide dehydrogenase Reduced Reduced Increased 11 b hydroxylase Reduced Increased Increased 17 a hydroxylase Reduced Increased Decreased P450 oxidoreductase Reduced Increased Decreased",
