          "correctOptionId": "opt-1",
          "explanation": "Aerial thrombosis and related consequences in APLA syndrome: Stroke-20%, TIA-11 %, Myocardial ischemia-10% Amaurosis fugax-7% Ref: Harrisons principles of internal medicine, 18th edition, Page 2737"
